  "detailed_description": "Survive and Revenge is an action and survival game set in a post-apocalyptic world. There are different levels to explore and survive.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Loot and Craft</h2>Resources are rare in the world and only by gathering and looting you can survive. Loot is needed to craft important items.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore and Fight</h2>Fight with mutants and outlaws to discover remote places.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Quests and story</h2>Follow the main story and decide for yourself which side quests you will complete.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Base and cities</h2>Buy a base and have the base expanded. Settlements can be inhabited by good or bad people.",
